* {{ill|Sakaibe no Marise|ja|境部摩理勢|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (did not participate in the campaign)
* {{ill|Prince Kume|ja|来目皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (did not complete the campaign)
* {{ill|Prince Tōma|ja|当麻皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (did not complete the campaign)
* {{ill|Nakatomi no Kuni|ja|中臣国|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Sakaibe no Umamaro|ja|境部雄摩侶|qq=draft|qq=draft}}

=== Deputy Generals ===
* {{ill|Hozumi no Suketari|ja|穂積祖足|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Kawabe no Neju|ja|河辺禰受|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Mononobe no Iyami no Ototo|ja|物部依網乙等|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Hada no Hiroba|ja|波多廣庭|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Ōmi no Ashikami no Iifuta|ja|近江脚身飯蓋|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Heguri no Ushi|ja|平群宇志|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Ōtomo no (unknown name)|ja|大伴某|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Ōyake no Ikusa|ja|大宅軍|qq=draft|qq=draft}}

