* {{ill|Heguri no Ushi|ja|平群宇志|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heguri no Ushi|qq=}}
* {{ill|Ōtomo no (unknown name)|ja|大伴某|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtomo no (unknown name)|qq=}}
