* {{ill|Kawabe no Neju|ja|河辺禰受|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kawabe no Neju|qq=}}
* {{ill|Mononobe no Iyami no Ototo|ja|物部依網乙等|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mononobe no Iyami no Ototo|qq=}}
